comments.body:
@Luap99 Since I have this Mac isolated anyway, would it be helpful to go hands-on and see if that makes debugging this any easier?

I aborted task 5452333704806400 right in the middle, stopping cleanup from running, so all the files should be there.

[This script](https://github.com/containers/automation/blob/main/mac_pw_pool/InstanceSSH.sh) may help you access `MacM1-6`, the "shared" ssh key is in the secret storage service.  Remember to set all [the expected envars](https://github.com/containers/podman/blob/main/contrib/cirrus/mac_setup.sh#L26-L38) before running tests.
